        <styleUrl>#vessel</styleUrl>
        <description>Branch: USN&#xA;Status: deployed — Conducting blockade operations in the Arabian Sea as part of ongoing deterrence efforts in the region, signaling U.S. commitment to maintaining freedom of navigation and countering Iranian maritime provocations.&#xA;Type: Aircraft Carrier Strike Group&#xA;Source: ai_intel</description>
